aming history.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/dd51b0a61620f127691f27d9b7f73c17.webp?t=1725109004\" width=16 height=16 /></span> Gameplay <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/dd51b0a61620f127691f27d9b7f73c17.webp?t=1725109004\" width=16 height=16 /></span></h2>Punch with the attack button or stomp enemies to defeat them. Collect hearts to power up Cham's punch into a <strong>long range whip attack</strong> and increase her ability to take hits!<br><br>Hold down the attack button to run if you need to make a speedy get away or need extra momentum for those long dangerous jumps! Search the stages for hidden keys and power-ups and try to take advantage of the <strong>shmup style bonus stages!</strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/7e9351157274cc26ac1321ec120bd5d5.apng?t=1725109004\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/7e9351157274cc26ac1321ec120bd5d5.poster.avif?t=1725109004\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=17 /></picture></span> Game Features <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/9accbf527f6cbb5463a1bad2a13a9d85.apng?t=1725109004\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2729380/extras/9accbf527f6cbb5463a1bad2a13a9d85.poster.avif?t=1725109004\" class=\"bb_img\" width=16 height=17 /></picture></span></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Classically challenging retro style platforming gameplay<br></li><li>Includes modernly convenient save system and mid stage checkpoints<br></li><li> Bonus stages, unlockable bonus level, and various hidden secrets throughout<br></li><li>8-bit sights and sounds that faithfully emulates the early era of handheld gaming<br></li><li>Catchy and nostalgic chiptune music.</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >How to access the menu</h2><strong>To access the game menu and manual, press select button on gamepad or shift key on keyboard.</strong>",
